column1: It's official!   We have officially launched the Crypto_Current_Sea Patreon group. It has been some time coming and we are extremely excited to be sharing some of the hottest information out there as soon as it gets created. Get the latest news so you don't miss a beat in this ever changing market. We can take you from a beginner all the way into a deep dive as far as you want go. Learn about all the airdrops with enough time to fulfill the requirements to get them. Learn to trade on your own time with a strategy that works for you. Learn which NFTs are worth their price and get the latest NFT auction updates.   You will have access to Musashi13. Musashi13 is: Beta & alpha tester for many protocols/teams including Aavegotchi, Good Ghosting, 1HIVE, Cipher, Libernet, Gala Games & Playform to name a few Developer and NFT creatorOfficial Aambassador for the Aavegotchi community(We are literally launching our Aambassador program at the same time as our Patreon so that our patrons will have first access to this new Gotchigang {It is free to join this team and will be highly beneficial and fun}). Learn about NFTs, DeFi, gamified finance, and so much more. We look forward to sharing this exciting journey and expect to see you there, flourishing. All Blessings,   Crypto_Current_Sea    #gotchigang   Aalpha leak: We will be training and selecting members of this group to develop, code, test, and build a community in which we will build our own projects. And trust me, these first projects are ground breaking and revolutionary. You will not want to miss out on this!
